Package: numbat
Title: Accurate reconstruction of copy number profiles in scRNA data using population haplotype phasing
Version: 0.0.0
Authors: Teng Gao, Peter Kharchenko
Maintainer: Teng Gao, tgao@g.harvard.edu
Description: Numbat is a computational method that infers copy number variations (CNVs) in cancer scRNA-Seq data and reconstructs the tumor phylogeny.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
